sequenceDiagram
  autonumber
  %% ARIA-NBV sequence template for training/serving/data-loading protocols.

  participant User as User / Evaluator
  participant Sup as Supervisor
  participant Policy as NBV Policy
  participant Store as Immutable VIN offline store
  participant Model as VIN Model
  participant AR as AR Overlay

  User->>Sup: start rollout(scene_id, budget)
  Sup->>Store: load observations + candidate set
  Store-->>Sup: sample, cameras, semidense points
  Sup->>Model: score candidates
  Model-->>Sup: predicted RRI map
  Sup->>Policy: select q_star
  Policy-->>Sup: next view action
  Sup->>AR: render pose / trajectory suggestion
  AR-->>User: visual NBV overlay
